        </p>
        
        <div class="hero-cta animate-fadeInUp delay-200">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">
            <span>Let's Connect</span>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#projects" class="btn-secondary">
            <span>View Work</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-social animate-fadeInUp delay-300">
          <a href="https://github.com/BaankeyBihari" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub">
            <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/baankeybihari" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn">
            <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/BaankeyBihari" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Twitter">
